{"tid":89897,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"儘管濕透了，披在身上的曼聯球衣決不輕易脫下","createTime":"2017-01-21T16:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T02:52:59.000Z","uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d94014a38e69c1a64a458e829dcb88e5b13c01e","tid":89897,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:17:37.000Z","msg":"曼聯正值多事之秋，內部問題成為大家的憂慮。新領隊摩連奴上任後面對種種難題，屋漏兼逢夜雨，外界普遍看淡曼聯此場硬仗。然而，本會仍堅守著「一條心，撐紅魔」的精神，與會員一起到北角城市花園酒店支持紅魔，以壯聲威。 <br />\n<br />\n本會首次移師到北角舉行活動，酒吧相當寬敞，環境舒適；光線調和，柔而不暗，最適合觀賞球賽。當晚早於七時半已有會員到場，及後更是絡繹不絕，把整間酒吧染成一片鮮紅。 <br />\n<br />\n比賽臨開始，司儀宣布出場陣容，幾位新加盟球員均正選上陣，會員熱切期待，興奮莫名。上半場比賽膠著，俱中場混戰。可是在完半場前，對手憑烏龍球先開記錄，紅魔半場落後。半場休息時，司儀播出曼城大勝曼聯6：1的精華片段，鼓舞士氣，振奮人心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然下半場對手再下一城，但球迷仍不放棄，放聲吶喊。球隊亦不負所望，手天使伊巴連入兩球追平，球迷喊聲震天，震臂高呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。可惜，球隊百密一疏，被對手頂入致勝入球，兵敗而回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。不過，球迷已經滿意球隊的表現，雖敗猶榮。賽後依舊有抽獎和大合照環節作結。 <br />\n<br />\n離開酒吧後，綿雨飄下，灑在漆黑街道上的球迷，儘管濕透了，披在身上的紅魔球衣決不輕易脫下...... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4033d5290fdd1c2427a90459254d7d5b8e308d0e","tid":89897,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8c0a0a5e77d25603ed18dcd0476a0fe8b487e5","tid":89897,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbce84b7e1edbfcaac2acebae39ee5829fa5ca37","tid":89897,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88b29a502f8ad90c96a9397a04eab030b45fe4e","tid":89897,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f8ad590bbee743e80ebcd25f7946ee1a7d00fd","tid":89897,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T01:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882aff362344847be63f41d170f8fc4f995a4775","tid":89897,"uid":30800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T02:01:06.000Z","msg":"手天使伊巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c60e9a6117af7bc6c7abd94f9eaba5e101a461f","tid":89897,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T02:03:19.000Z","msg":"魚拉特 啪啪啪"},{"pid":"6bac21d863e58e45bb2bf4a7499414c086d0b164","tid":89897,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:22:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魚拉特 啪啪啪</blockquote>"},{"pid":"71a4a8e1c51a09fa0f5f4a9e92a337c33dcf5a88","tid":89897,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:52:59.000Z","msg":"G"}]}